    <p>
      <em>Questions to Consider:</em>
    </p>
    <p>
      <ul xml:id="m79872-fs-idm223882224">
        <li>
          <p>How do you prepare yourself and your environment for successful studying?</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>What study strategies will be most beneficial to you?</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>What are learning preferences and strategies, and how can you leverage those to your advantage?</p>
        </li>
